messages.text: Hey did you have dinner plans for tonight? I was thinking we go to the Crafter.
I don't know man, that sounds really crazy.
How about we just go to the other place instead?
That's dumb. The Crafter is where it's at. Remember how last time we saw all that cool stuff there? We saw the fireworks.
We even saw Zuckerberg there -- Zuck knows where it's at, dude. I know he wears the same T-Shirt every day, but he knows his food. You should really go.
Zuck is super lame. And you are too for liking his taste in food.
